snippet.title: FUNNY DOGS + WATER = You LAUGH (Funny DOG VIDEOS compilation)
snippet.description:
These dogs really love water and summer! I'm sure they will make you laugh super hard! This funny dog compilation is the hardest try not to laugh challenge ever! These dogs and puppies are so ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
